
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>鼎新數智 — 讓更多人智慧工作樂享生活</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@300;400;500;600;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --max-w: 1320px;
      --blue: #1a7fd4;
      --blue-bright: #3db3ff;
      --cyan: #00d4ff;
      --bg-dark: #060c18;
      --bg-mid: #091220;
      --bg-light: #f2f5f9;
      --border: rgba(30,90,180,0.3);
      --text: rgba(255,255,255,0.88);
      --text-dim: rgba(255,255,255,0.58);
      --text-muted: rgba(255,255,255,0.35);
      --hero-bg: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,');
    }

    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      color: var(--text);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    .container-main {
      max-width: var(--max-w);
      margin-inline: auto;
      padding-inline: 40px;
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       NAV
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .site-nav {
      position: fixed;
      inset-block-start: 0;
      inset-inline: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      height: 56px;
      background: rgba(6, 12, 24, 0.93);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);

      & .nav-inner {
        max-width: var(--max-w);
        margin-inline: auto;
        padding-inline: 40px;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 32px;
      }

      & .nav-brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        text-decoration: none;
        flex-shrink: 0;

        & .brand-box {
          width: 26px;
          height: 26px;
          background: var(--blue);
          border-radius: 4px;
          display: grid;
          place-items: center;
          font-size: 11px;
          font-weight: 900;
          color: #fff;
        }

        & span {
          font-size: 15px;
          font-weight: 700;
          color: #fff;
          letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
      }

      & .nav-menu {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        list-style: none;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        flex: 1;
        gap: 0;

        & li a {
          display: block;
          padding: 0 14px;
          line-height: 56px;
          font-size: 13px;
          color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);
          text-decoration: none;
          white-space: nowrap;
          transition: color 0.18s;

          &:hover { color: var(--cyan); }
        }
      }

      & .nav-actions {
        display: flex;
        gap: 8px;
        flex-shrink: 0;

        & .btn-nav {
          padding: 5px 15px;
          font-size: 12.5px;
          border-radius: 4px;
          font-family: inherit;
          cursor: pointer;
          transition: all 0.18s;
          border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
          background: transparent;
          color: rgba(255,255,255,0.62);

          &:hover { border-color: var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); }

          &.primary {
            background: var(--blue);
            border-color: var(--blue);
            color: #fff;

            &:hover { background: var(--blue-bright); border-color: var(--blue-bright); }
          }
        }
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       HERO
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .hero {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 100px 24px 80px;
      background: #000 var(--hero-bg) center center / cover no-repeat;

      &::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(
          180deg,
          rgba(0,0,0,0.22) 0%,
          rgba(0,5,20,0.38) 55%,
          rgba(0,5,20,0.72) 100%
        );
      }

      & .hero-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 2;
        max-width: 860px;
      }

      & .hero-eyebrow {
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 5px;
        color: var(--cyan);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 28px;
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.15s both;
      }

      & .hero-title {
        font-size: clamp(38px, 5.5vw, 68px);
        font-weight: 900;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1.18;
        margin-bottom: 36px;
        text-shadow: 0 2px 40px rgba(0,100,220,0.5);
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.3s both;
      }

      & .hero-body {
        font-size: 15.5px;
        line-height: 2;
        color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
        max-width: 720px;
        margin: 0 auto 14px;
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.45s both;
      }

      & .hero-tagline {
        font-size: 14.5px;
        color: rgba(0,212,255,0.8);
        margin-bottom: 48px;
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.55s both;
      }

      & .hero-ctas {
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        justify-content: center;
        animation: fadeUp 0.9s 0.65s both;
      }
    }

    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       BUTTONS
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .btn-primary-site {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: var(--blue);
      color: #fff;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.22s;
      letter-spacing: 0.3px;

      &:hover {
        background: var(--blue-bright);
        color: #fff;
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(41,170,255,0.4);
      }
    }

    .btn-ghost-site {
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: transparent;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.22);
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-size: 14px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      transition: all 0.22s;

      &:hover {
        border-color: var(--cyan);
        color: var(--cyan);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       SECTION COMMONS
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .sec-label {
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: 4px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--cyan);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 14px;

      &.dark { color: var(--blue); }
    }

    .sec-title {
      font-size: clamp(22px, 2.8vw, 38px);
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.28;
      margin-bottom: 18px;

      & .accent { color: var(--cyan); }
      &.on-light { color: #0d1b33; }
    }

    .sec-sub {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text-dim);

      &.on-light { color: #4a5568; }
    }

    /* scroll fade-in */
    .fi {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(26px);
      transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease;

      &.in { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       MISSION SECTION
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .mission-section {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #020810 0%, var(--bg-dark) 100%);
      padding-block: 96px;
    }

    .mission-body {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 2.05;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      margin-bottom: 22px;
    }

    .statement-card {
      background: rgba(26, 100, 200, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(26, 100, 200, 0.22);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      padding: 26px 32px;
      font-size: 14.5px;
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 2.05;
      color: var(--text);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .cap-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--border);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 48px;

      & .cap-col {
        background: rgba(8,18,38,0.9);
        padding: 26px 22px;
        transition: background 0.2s;

        &:hover { background: rgba(26,100,200,0.1); }
      }

      & .cap-title {
        font-size: 13.5px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        padding-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      & .cap-desc {
        font-size: 12.5px;
        line-height: 1.82;
        color: var(--text-dim);
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       TIMELINE (light bg)
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .timeline-section {
      background: var(--bg-light);
      padding-block: 96px;
    }

    .tl-wrap {
      position: relative;
      padding-left: 140px;
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .tl-spine {
      position: absolute;
      left: 60px;
      top: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--blue) 0%, var(--blue-bright) 100%);
    }

    .tl-item {
      position: relative;
      padding: 22px 0 22px 32px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(26,100,200,0.12);

      &:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

      & .tl-year {
        position: absolute;
        left: -138px;
        top: 24px;
        width: 56px;
        text-align: right;
        font-size: 12.5px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--blue);
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }

      & .tl-dot {
        position: absolute;
        left: -72px;
        top: 28px;
        width: 13px;
        height: 13px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--blue);
        border: 3px solid var(--bg-light);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--blue);
      }

      & .tl-badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 2px 10px;
        border-radius: 3px;
        font-size: 10.5px;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.8px;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 7px;
      }

      & .tl-phase {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #0d1b33;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      & .tl-text {
        font-size: 13.5px;
        line-height: 1.78;
        color: #4a5568;
      }
    }

    .tl-statement {
      margin-top: 48px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e6efff, #eef5ff);
      border-left: 4px solid var(--blue);
      border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
      padding: 28px 32px;
      font-size: 14.5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 2;
      color: #1a2a4a;
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       STRENGTH (dark)
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .strength-section {
      background: var(--bg-mid);
      padding-block: 96px;
    }

    .strength-body {
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 2;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .geo-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
      gap: 40px;
      align-items: start;
      margin-top: 56px;
    }

    .map-box {
      background: rgba(4,12,30,0.85);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      overflow: hidden;

      & svg { width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }
    }

    .offices-panel {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 9px;
    }

    .office-row {
      background: rgba(10,22,50,0.7);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 13px 18px;
      transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
      cursor: default;

      &:hover {
        border-color: var(--cyan);
        background: rgba(0,212,255,0.06);
      }

      & .o-country {
        font-size: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--cyan);
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }

      & .o-name {
        font-size: 13.5px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 3px;
      }

      & .o-detail {
        font-size: 11.5px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       STATS
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .stats-section {
      background: #07101f;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-block: 80px;
    }

    .stats-lead { font-size: 12.5px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .stats-headline { font-size: 17px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); margin-bottom: 52px; }

    .stats-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);

      & .stat-col {
        padding: 0 40px;
        text-align: center;
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);

        &:first-child { padding-left: 0; }
        &:last-child { border-right: none; }
      }
    }

    .stat-num {
      font-size: 72px;
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--blue-bright), var(--cyan));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-size: 13.5px;
      line-height: 1.72;
      color: var(--text-dim);
    }

    .stat-note {
      font-size: 11.5px;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      margin-top: 5px;
    }

    .stats-detail {
      margin-top: 52px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;

      & .sd-row {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);

        &:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
      }

      & .sd-cell {
        padding: 18px 24px;
        font-size: 13px;
        line-height: 1.78;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        border-right: 1px solid var(--border);

        &:last-child { border-right: none; }

        & strong { color: #fff; }
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       CLOSING
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .closing-section {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg-mid) 0%, #030912 100%);
      padding-block: 96px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .closing-body {
      max-width: 820px;
      margin: 0 auto 22px;
      font-size: 14.5px;
      line-height: 2.05;
      color: var(--text-dim);
      text-align: left;
    }

    .closing-card {
      margin-top: 56px;
      background: rgba(26,100,200,0.09);
      border: 1px solid rgba(26,100,200,0.28);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 48px 56px;

      & p {
        font-size: 17px;
        line-height: 1.92;
        color: var(--text);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      & .sub-p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      & .cta-row {
        margin-top: 30px;
        display: flex;
        gap: 14px;
        justify-content: center;
      }
    }

    /* ──────────────────────────────
       FOOTER
    ────────────────────────────── */
    .site-footer {
      background: #02060e;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-block: 56px 28px;

      & .footer-brand-name {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      & .footer-tagline {
        font-size: 12.5px;
        line-height: 1.72;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      & .footer-col h4 {
        font-size: 11.5px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-dim);
        letter-spacing: 1px;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }

      & .footer-col ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 0;

        & li { margin-bottom: 8px; }

        & a {
          color: var(--text-muted);
          text-decoration: none;
          font-size: 13px;
          transition: color 0.18s;

          &:hover { color: var(--cyan); }
        }
      }

      & .footer-bottom {
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
        padding-top: 20px;
        margin-top: 48px;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        font-size: 11.5px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="site-nav">
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="#" class="nav-brand">
        <div class="brand-box">鼎</div>
        <span>鼎新數智</span>
      </a>
      <ul class="nav-menu">
        <li><a href="#">人才招募</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">關於我們</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">產品</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">行業</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">解決方案</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">客戶案例</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">合作夥伴</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">知識庫</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">新聞中心</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">社會責任</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <button class="btn-nav">🔍</button>
        <button class="btn-nav">聯絡我們</button>
        <button class="btn-nav primary">免費體驗</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero" id="top">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Digiwin — 鼎新數智</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">讓更多人<br>智慧工作　樂享生活</h1>
      <p class="hero-body">
        我們相信，科技最終價值在於釋放人的潛能，<br>
        突破人力與能力的限制，創新於無解之題、創值於無能之處。
      </p>
      <p class="hero-body">
        在 AI 重新定義產業運作的時代，鼎新數智已從軟體服務商，往 AI 原生企業基礎設施提供者轉型進化，並將持續以此角色，攜手產業夥伴與客戶，成為 AI 轉型路上的引路人，陪伴企業穩健邁向智慧運營的新階段。
      </p>
      <p class="hero-tagline">一起用數智實現創想　實現「讓更多人智慧工作，樂享生活」的美好願景。</p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="#mission" class="btn-primary-site">探索我們的使命</a>
        <a href="#strength" class="btn-ghost-site">了解布局實力</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <section class="mission-section" id="mission">
    <div class="container-main">

      <div class="text-center mb-5 fi">
        <div class="sec-label">我們的使命</div>
        <h2 class="sec-title">用數據和智能技術　<span class="accent">創新生產力</span></h2>
        <p class="sec-sub" style="max-width:820px; margin-inline:auto;">
          企業的茁壯，總是在一步一腳印中留下時代的印記；而鼎新一路走來的成功軌跡，則奠基於始終秉持的「創新、尊重、專業」企業經營理念。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fi">
        <p class="mission-body">鼎新的誕生源於對產業浪潮下的創新轉型的回應。1980年代的企業數位化剛萌芽，導入成本高、開發週期長、失敗率極高，使資訊化成為少數企業才能負擔的工程。創辦人孫藹彬先生懷抱讓更多企業得以實現資訊化管理的遠見，創立「鼎新電腦」，以ERP套裝軟體的創新模式，讓數位化成為普及、可推廣、可長期維運的企業基礎建設。這也是我們一路走來最重要的起點——以洞察時代挑戰、打造可實際落地的技術來回應企業需求。</p>
        <p class="mission-body">此後，每一段產業歷史的轉折，都成為我們與企業共同前行的軌跡。從IFRS、個資法、工業4.0到新冠疫情衝擊、ESG合規壓力、台商出海布局、乃至近年的關稅與匯率變動、AI轉型，我們總是在風口來臨的第一時間，集結合作夥伴，快速推出對應解方，協助企業在變局中維持營運穩定、保持成長動能。</p>
        <p class="mission-body">逾四十五年來，鼎新已獲超過50,000家客戶的肯定與實證，現在的「鼎新數智」，則是用全新的視角看待數據和智能技術，以數智平台乘載豐富的數智化應用場景，匯聚我們的客戶、合作夥伴以數智實現創想。</p>
      </div>

      <div class="statement-card fi">
